description: [``botocore``] This release adds support to view Network firewall proxy appliances attached to an existing NAT Gateway via DescribeNatGateways API NatGatewayAttachedAppliance structure.
[``botocore``] Network Firewall release of the Proxy feature.
[``botocore``] Add support for policy operations on the S3_POLICY and BEDROCK_POLICY policy type.
[``botocore``] Adds support for new route53 feature: accelerated recovery.
